title: A Celeb Gave Amy’s Son a Birthday Gift + Fantasy Draft of TV Themes + A Listener Calls Amy Out For Being ‘Fake’
itunes:title: A Celeb Gave Amy’s Son a Birthday Gift + Fantasy Draft of TV Themes + A Listener Calls Amy Out For Being ‘Fake’
description:
Amy’s son got a really cool birthday gift from a country artist and talked about how he wanted to “text God”. We do our Fantasy Draft of TV Themes and a caller shares why she thinks Amy has been fake on the show.
